Investment Management


Leverage our conflict-free service model, global reach, and strong jurisdictional knowledge for your corporate trust and other business ventures.





For more than a century, Wilmington Trust has been a leader in corporate trust services, serving on some of the largest and highest profile transactions. As a unique provider due to our non-creditor role in transactions, we are able to act as a neutral, impartial Trustee or Agent, taking a creative and collaborative approach to making your transaction a success.


Talk to us about how we can help you achieve the desired results from your corporate and institutional business ventures.

Capital Markets Agency Services
Benefit from our extensive involvement in default/bankruptcy, loan agency, corporate debt/high-yield, M&A, and other capital markets transactions.
Capital Markets Structured Finance
Foster success with your structured finance transactions through our comprehensive administrative and trustee services.
Institutional Custody/Administrative Services
Count on our experienced staff to manage your back-office, operational, and virtually all administrative/institutional custody tasks, so you can devote your time to other important aspects of your business.
Special Purpose Vehicle Administration
Let our SPV management experience in the world's leading jurisdictions help you reinforce a substantive presence. 
Entity Management
Access our extensive capabilities in the establishment and operation of many types of structures in jurisdictions around the globe.
Retirement Services
Enhance your role as a TPA with a firm providing independent, institutional services – and over 65 years of experience serving the retirement industry.
Investment Management
Bolster your portfolio and capital position through our institutional asset management solutions, designed to maximize investment opportunities.







